OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Ffading during the evening and most
OL,7,Fplaces becoming dry with some clear
OL,8,Fspells here and there. Light winds.
OL,9,FTurning chilly under starry skies.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FDry for many on bank holiday
OL,12,FMonday with bright or sunny spells
OL,13,Fdeveloping, particularly during the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Temperatures close to
OL,15,Fnormal for early May.
