OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers on Tuesday, but with some
OL,7,Fsunnier spells emerging. Similar on
OL,8,FWednesday and Thursday with variable
OL,9,Famounts of cloud. Feeling chillier
OL,10,Fthan recent days with decreasing
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
